---
Show persisted event history

Usage: mxr history [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --category <CATEGORY>  
      --level <LEVEL>        
      --limit <LIMIT>        [default: 50]
      --format <FORMAT>      [possible values: table, json, jsonl, csv, ids]
  -h, --help                 Print help
